## Handoff

When status is `ready-for-planning`, run `/plan <slug>`. The planner treats:
- `srs.md` / `frd.md` → the **requirements source** (`spec.md` cites these IDs);
- `sdd.md` / `tdd.md` → **architectural direction & constraints** (re-verified only where planning
  genuinely diverges);
- `research-report.md` → **risk and competitor context**.
